interpretation: The Flag of Taiwan represents the island nation's rich history and unique identity. This card symbolizes the pursuit of independence and self-determination, as well as the pride that comes with asserting one's cultural identity. It is a reminder to embrace diversity and honor our differences, as they are what make us unique and special. This card encourages you to stay true to yourself, even in the face of adversity, and to never lose sight of the values that make you who you are. It is a symbol of hope and resilience, a reminder that no matter how difficult the journey may be, there is always a light at the end of the tunnel. When this card appears in a reading, it suggests that the querent is on the right path towards achieving their goals and should continue to pursue their dreams with determination and courage.
